{"id":635046,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/02/【立此存照】小杭日记：妈妈走了-爸爸去找妈妈了/","date":"2020-02-09T12:07:26Z","modified":"2020-02-09T17:05:38Z","title":"【立此存照】小杭日记：妈妈走了 爸爸去找妈妈了 我也感染了","content":"<p>近日，一位豆瓣网友@小杭（来自武汉）的几条“豆瓣广播”在网上热传，她一家人的经历令不少人看后落泪：小杭的父母已因“新冠肺炎”而相继去世，小杭自己目前也出现了疑似感染症状。</p>\n<p>这是流传于网络的几张<a href=\"https://twitter.com/LifetimeUSCN/status/1226201189651488771\">网友截图</a>：</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/EQRXex-XUAIsvcf.jpeg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-635047\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/EQRXex-XUAIsvcf.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"610\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/EQRXex-XUAIsvcf.jpeg 664w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/EQRXex-XUAIsvcf-221x300.jpeg 221w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/EQRXexrWoAg7KQe.jpeg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-635049\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/EQRXexrWoAg7KQe.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"672\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/EQRXexrWoAg7KQe.jpeg 603w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/EQRXexrWoAg7KQe-201x300.jpeg 201w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/EQRXexsW4AAmcj9.jpeg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-635048\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/EQRXexsW4AAmcj9.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"254\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/EQRXexsW4AAmcj9.jpeg 679w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/EQRXexsW4AAmcj9-300x170.jpeg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p>1月19日，小杭的豆瓣广播上开始出现了关于“武汉肺炎”的记录，从描述上看小杭家离武汉华南海鲜城不到500米。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-635050\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记.png 1390w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记-300x57.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记-1024x196.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记-768x147.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记-1080x207.png 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1390px) 100vw, 1390px\" /></a></p>\n<p>1月21日，仅两天后，小杭尚在抢购口罩的同时，她的母亲就出现了发烧症状。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记2-7.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-635051\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记2-7.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"152\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记2-7.png 1364w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记2-7-300x83.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记2-7-1024x284.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记2-7-768x213.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记2-7-1080x299.png 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>1月23日，武汉封城的当天，小杭发出了那条求救信息，与此同时她母亲的症状变得越发严重。在此期间，小杭也是想尽办法为她的母亲进行治疗。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记3-5.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-635052\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记3-5.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"97\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记3-5.png 1372w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记3-5-300x53.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记3-5-1024x181.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记3-5-768x135.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记3-5-1080x190.png 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记4-4.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-635053\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记4-4.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"243\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记4-4.png 1368w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记4-4-300x132.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记4-4-1024x452.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记4-4-768x339.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记4-4-1080x477.png 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a> <a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记5-3.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-635054\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记5-3.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"311\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记5-3.png 1366w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记5-3-300x170.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记5-3-1024x579.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记5-3-768x434.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记5-3-1080x610.png 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>1月24日，小杭的妈妈被送到医院，小杭家人要抢在24点前看医生，因为“只有看上医生，才能被确诊，才可能被收治入院”。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记6-4.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-635055\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记6-4.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"241\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记6-4.png 1376w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记6-4-300x131.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记6-4-1024x448.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记6-4-768x336.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记6-4-1080x473.png 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>而当天小杭的妈妈就开始尝试办理住院，从小杭的描述看，当地医院的医护力量严重不足，而父亲和自己因为与母亲的近距离接触，存在着被传染的极高可能性。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记7-3.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-635056\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记7-3.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"348\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记7-3.png 1370w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记7-3-300x190.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记7-3-1024x647.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记7-3-768x485.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记7-3-1080x683.png 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>1月25日，小杭的朋友告诉她自己的外婆在家“中风”因没有足够的医疗救助而去世。当天小杭母亲也没有及时消息回复，令小杭和小杭父亲无比担心。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记8-2.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-635057\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记8-2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"340\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记8-2.png 1386w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记8-2-300x186.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记8-2-1024x634.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记8-2-768x475.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记8-2-1080x669.png 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>1月26日，小杭母亲的情况已变得更加复杂，医院原本想将其转移至金银潭医院，结果“一问三不知”。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记9.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-635058\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记9.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"522\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记9.png 1400w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记9-300x285.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记9-1024x971.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记9-768x729.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记9-1080x1024.png 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>1月27日，小杭父亲做了CT检查，已确认感染。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记10-2.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-635059\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记10-2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"105\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记10-2.png 1368w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记10-2-300x57.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记10-2-1024x196.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记10-2-768x147.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记10-2-1080x207.png 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>1月28日，小杭的母亲去世，离出现“发烧症状”仅一周的时间。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记11-1.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-635060\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记11-1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"203\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记11-1.png 1364w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记11-1-300x111.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记11-1-1024x378.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记11-1-768x284.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记11-1-1080x399.png 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>1月29，还来不及悲痛，小杭又带着父亲四处寻医，希望“保护爸爸到最后”。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记12-2.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-635061\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记12-2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"296\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记12-2.png 1366w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记12-2-300x162.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记12-2-1024x552.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记12-2-768x414.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记12-2-1080x582.png 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>但两日的医院体验，让小杭觉得“医院才是最危险的地方”：太容易交叉感染并且医护力量严重不足，自己太担心“妈妈的悲剧重演”，太后悔带着“最需要营养和休息的父亲四处奔波”。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记13-1.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-635062\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记13-1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"306\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记13-1.png 1388w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记13-1-300x167.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记13-1-1024x570.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记13-1-768x427.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记13-1-1080x601.png 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a>1月31日，距离“知道妈妈生病的第十天”，小杭仍在努力救父亲，明明身处“地狱”，但那两天武汉的天气给人一种“岁月静好盛世太平”的错觉。小杭无比怀念曾经平凡的生活。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记14-1.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-635063\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记14-1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"443\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记14-1.png 1374w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记14-1-300x241.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记14-1-1024x824.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记14-1-768x618.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记14-1-1080x869.png 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>2月2日，小杭父亲的情况变差，最终还是住进了医院。父亲在病房里“拼命赶我走”。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记15-1.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-635064\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记15-1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"221\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记15-1.png 1368w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记15-1-300x121.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记15-1-1024x412.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记15-1-768x309.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记15-1-1080x434.png 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>2月3日，小杭写下了一段纪念母亲的文字并写道“只是我要求求你，保佑爸爸。现在，还不能带走他。我每天都在拼了命的救他，并后悔没有如此的保护你。”</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记16.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-635065\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记16.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"428\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记16.png 1420w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记16-300x234.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记16-1024x798.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记16-768x598.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记16-1080x841.png 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>2月5日，小杭出现了发烧症状，担心自己也受到了感染，与此同时医院传来父亲病危的消息要求她赶去签字。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记17-1.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-635066\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记17-1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"173\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记17-1.png 1370w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记17-1-300x94.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记17-1-1024x321.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记17-1-768x241.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记17-1-1080x339.png 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>2月6日，小杭陆续也收到了许多来自各地热情的帮助，但这种救助对小杭时间的大量挤占也让她感觉很累更绝望。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记18-1.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-635067\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记18-1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"495\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记18-1.png 1386w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记18-1-300x270.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记18-1-1024x922.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记18-1-768x692.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记18-1-1080x972.png 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>2月7日，在好心人士和同事的帮助下，小杭父亲得到了转院治疗的机会，但父亲的情况已变得很差。小杭已经非常不忍看到呼吸衰弱的父亲所承受的苦痛。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记19-1.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-635068\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记19-1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"222\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记19-1.png 1380w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记19-1-300x121.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记19-1-1024x414.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记19-1-768x311.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记19-1-1080x437.png 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记20-1.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-635069\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记20-1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"117\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记20-1.png 1368w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记20-1-300x64.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记20-1-1024x219.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记20-1-768x164.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记20-1-1080x231.png 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记21-1.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-635070\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记21-1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"155\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记21-1.png 1358w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记21-1-300x84.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记21-1-1024x288.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记21-1-768x216.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记21-1-1080x304.png 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>2月8日，小杭同时得到了两条噩耗：父亲的去世以及自己的感染。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记22-1.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-635071\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记22-1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"201\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记22-1.png 1372w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记22-1-300x110.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记22-1-1024x375.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记22-1-768x281.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记22-1-1080x395.png 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>2月9日，还需要“安排各种后事”的小杭带着“我要活下去”的执念正继续地与疾病进行抗争。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记24.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-635077\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记24.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"189\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记24.png 1360w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记24-300x103.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记24-1024x352.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记24-768x264.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记24-1080x372.png 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记23.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-635072\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记23.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"312\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记23.png 1378w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记23-300x170.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记23-1024x581.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记23-768x436.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/小杭日记23-1080x613.png 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><a class=\"st_tag internal_tag\" title=\"Posts tagged with CDS档案\" href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/tag/cds%e6%a1%a3%e6%a1%88/\" rel=\"tag\">CDS档案</a>|<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/space/%E6%AD%A6%E6%B1%89%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E\">武汉肺炎</a></strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"size-thumbnail wp-image-632597 aligncenter\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/01/wuhanfeiyan-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/01/wuhanfeiyan-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/01/wuhanfeiyan-50x50.jpg 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></p>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18271,38912,39486,39707],"tags":[39763,39762,10721,39646,13381,39648,39611]}